1. Install NEURON with python2.7 - see INSTALL-neuron for details

2. Install version of SpatialKappa from "neuron" branch

3. Install py4j
   easy_install py4j
   # easy_install  --install-dir=/disk/scratch/sterratt/lib/python2.7/site-packages/ py4j

4. Run make to produce .class files

5. Check paths to NEURON and SpatialKappa jar file in nrn-kappa

6. Try

   cd test/test_ca_pulse_var
   ../../nrn-kappa -i test_ca_pulse.py